<title>AUSTRALIA: Australia needs more labour market reform - Costello.</title>
<headline>Australia needs more labour market reform - Costello.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Australian Treasurer Peter Costello echoed Reserve Bank Governor Ian Macfarlane on Friday and said Australia needed nore labour market reform.</p>
<p>English-speaking countries such as the United States, Britain and New Zealand had freer labour market systems and notably lower unemployment rates than continental Europe, Costello told a football club lunch.</p>
<p>&quot;We would want to move much further in the direction that those Anglo countries have taken,&quot; Costello said.</p>
